OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSchools to count thousands 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fmore children as absent    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Thousands more children will be classed
OL,6, as "persistently" absent from school as
OL,7, part of Welsh government plans to      
OL,8, tackle an attendance "crisis".         
OL,10,FIt is hoped that redefining persistent 
OL,11,Fto include pupils missing 10% of school
OL,12,Fsessions - compared to the current 20% 
OL,13,F- will address the problem earlier.    
OL,15,FThe move will bring Wales in line with 
OL,16,Fwhat is happening in England.          
OL,18,FWhile supporting families to get       
OL,19,Fchildren back in class is key, fines   
OL,20,Fwill be brought in as "a last resort". 
